OL,6,GA campaign to retain traditional TV and
OL,7,Gradio broadcasting hit rocky ground
OL,8,Gthis week after the BBC's
OL,9,Gdirector-general said he wanted to push
OL,10,Gtoward internet-only distribution of
OL,11,Gthe BBC.
OL,13,FOn Sunday, broadcast infrastructure
OL,14,Fcompany Arqiva rebooted its Broadcast
OL,15,F2040+ campaign lobbying decision-makers
OL,16,Fwith the publication of a poll of
OL,17,Fvoters in marginal parliamentary seats.
OL,3,CCampaign to save terrestrial TV hits a
OL,4,Csnag
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G1/14
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35302
SC,0002
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1672876098
OL,6,FThe poll found 75% of voters wanted
OL,7,Ftheir MP to actively support the
OL,8,Fcontinued provision of digital
OL,9,Fterrestrial TV and radio. This prompted
OL,10,FMPs including North Devon's Selaine
OL,11,FSaxby to speak out in favour of
OL,12,Fprotecting services.
OL,14,FThe future use of frequencies for
OL,15,FFreeview is in doubt beyond 2030. Usage
OL,16,Fof terrestrial TV frequencies is
OL,17,Fco-ordinated internationally by the
OL,18,FITU, a United Nations agency.
OL,3,CCampaign to save terrestrial TV hits a
OL,4,Csnag
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G2/14
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35303
SC,0003
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1672876098
OL,6,FNext November, delegates from around
OL,7,Fthe world will be meeting in Dubai for
OL,8,Fthe World Radiocommunications
OL,9,FConference (WRC) to discuss how to
OL,10,Fallocate frequencies in the next
OL,11,Fdecade.
OL,13,FThis follows a decade that has seen the
OL,14,F700 MHz and 800 MHz frequency band sold
OL,15,Foff to mobile operators to enhance
OL,16,Ftheir 4G and 5G networks. Mobile
OL,17,Foperators are now interested in
OL,18,Facquiring further spectrum.
OL,3,CCampaign to save terrestrial TV hits a
OL,4,Csnag
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G3/14
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35304
SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1672876098
OL,6,FThe BBC's director-general Tim Davie
OL,7,Fhas today told the Royal Television
OL,8,FSociety that he sees the BBC moving
OL,9,Faway from traditional broadcast
OL,10,Fplatforms in favour of going
OL,11,Fonline-only. In his speech, Mr Davie
OL,12,Fcalled on the industry to help educate
OL,13,Fusers to ensure no-one is left out.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Arqiva's Broadcast 2040+
OL,16,Fcampaign has enrolled charities
OL,17,Fincluding Silver Voices and consumer
OL,18,Fgroup Voice of the Listener and Viewer
OL,19,F(VLV) to lobby for services to remain
OL,20,Fhow they are.
OL,3,CCampaign to save terrestrial TV hits a
OL,4,Csnag
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G4/14
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35305
SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1672876098
OL,6,FWhereas public broadcasters in Europe
OL,7,Fhave joined calls to preserve TV
OL,8,Ffrequencies for cultural and
OL,9,Fbroadcasting use, the BBC has stayed
OL,10,Fsilent. It has not participated in
OL,11,FArqiva's Broadcast 2040+ campaign.
OL,13,FThe BBC has told Ofcom that a position
OL,14,Fof 'no change' will give it time to
OL,15,Fmigrate viewers from terrestrial TV to
OL,16,Fthe internet, underpinning its intent
OL,17,Fto withdraw from traditional broadcast
OL,18,Fplatforms.
OL,3,CCampaign to save terrestrial TV hits a
OL,4,Csnag
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G5/14
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35306
SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1672876098
OL,6,FThe ITU splits the world in multiple
OL,7,Fregions. The UK is included in ITU
OL,8,FRegion 1 and the decision for region 1
OL,9,Fwill apply to all countries within it.
OL,10,FMany organisations have already set out
OL,11,Ftheir position.
OL,13,FThe European Commission has responded
OL,14,Fto lobbying by broadcasters and
OL,15,Foperators in the EU by saying
OL,16,Fterrestrial TV frequencies should be
OL,17,Fleft alone.
OL,3,CCampaign to save terrestrial TV hits a
OL,4,Csnag
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G6/14
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35307
SC,0007
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1672876098
OL,6,FBut that won't necessarily mean the
OL,7,Fcurrent terrestrial TV system will
OL,8,Fremain: Broadcasters are actively
OL,9,Ftrialling new technologies including 5G
OL,10,FBroadcast as possible successors to
OL,11,Fcurrent terrestrial TV services.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the African Union of
OL,13,FBroadcasters has also supported a 'no
OL,14,Fchange' motion.
OL,16,FThe UK doesn't yet have an official
OL,17,Fposition. Virgin Media O2, Vodafone, BT
OL,18,Fand Three are demanding Ofcom support a
OL,19,Freallocation of the remaining TV
OL,20,Ffrequencies.
OL,3,CCampaign to save terrestrial TV hits a
OL,4,Csnag
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G7/14
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35308
SC,0008
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1672876098
OL,6,FAs viewers in South East England and
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland will know when they
OL,8,Ffind non-UK services on their radio or
OL,9,FTV, broadcast airwaves do not stop at
OL,10,Fborders. On its own, the UK's position
OL,11,Fwill not carry much weight and is still
OL,12,Finterlinked with decisions made in the
OL,13,FEU.
OL,15,FThe final outcome one way or the other
OL,16,Fwon't be known until December 2023.
OL,3,CCampaign to save terrestrial TV hits a
OL,4,Csnag
