OL,6,FThe Government has said it will allow
OL,7,Fbroadcasting licences for Freeview's
OL,8,Fmultiplexes to run until 2035, but with
OL,9,Fan early termination clause effective
OL,10,Fbeyond 2030.
OL,12,FIt's also asked Ofcom to review digital
OL,13,Fterrestrial television in 2024,
OL,14,Fimmediately after the ITU WRC-23
OL,15,Fconference outcome. Its report will
OL,16,Fdetermine whether licences will be
OL,17,Fterminated earlier rather than later.
OL,3,CCampaign to save terrestrial TV hits a
OL,4,Csnag
